{"tid":146022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得LFO","createTime":"2017-03-06T16:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T17:40:35.000Z","uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c834978038c079ef7cbdb09ffe2596b281f2bf8","tid":146022,"uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"當年第一隻課金既game，買卡包，買筆盒，買漫畫，排3個鐘動漫節買限量版<br />\n有把金色劍打人會著火，比人昆咗就大叫call gm<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/004525_5eef74151e8329f224951eddd9557def.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F004525_5eef74151e8329f224951eddd9557def.jpg&h=fee7447f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最叻lv 1xx 天魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc0ec4eb63e66998ff5503837b4df7adfddbe4","tid":146022,"uid":11381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"記得有一排有得用掃把bug<br />\n打得贏高自己好多lv嘅關"},{"pid":"b8b3e2e4dfd59860de296a3e20f79a819885dac3","tid":146022,"uid":83084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"記得果陣game入面同人交易<br />\n諗住人地比埋個屋企電話我無死啦<br />\n點知係電話講完我個卡number之後佢就cut左線<br />\n自此我狂打個電話追佢數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween 把金色劍係咪皇者之劍?"},{"pid":"07e1814900c1e5a210e812487d6e7c2efcfe02c9","tid":146022,"uid":71000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"以為有外掛仔bug錢<br />\n勁貴收一件皇者裝<br />\n之後賣兩三件比佢 就爆左上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b5dc1de097d9d61ee41e53a7c132dd9631357f","tid":146022,"uid":27413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"其實幾好玩可惜3頭身太柒同個名唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有玩都唔敢俾人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfafb105b877466a18ae1c4312a1865752b9a63e","tid":146022,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"Peak top10 留名"},{"pid":"5e431f1893cb4c3e0bbefc38441c0d06376c4dce","tid":146022,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"我都玩peak<br />\n最記得剛更新完有天地人尊<br />\n我fd叫我玩<br />\n我game都未down就買第一包卡即中人尊<br />\n雖然唔係勁但好威威<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後有咩邪鬼天魔<br />\n就係未玩過deep<br />\n<br />\n天魔就抽番嚟<br />\n又係單買一包中勁high<br />\n之後用其他卡起左銀色刮個part<br />\n痴落用咗天魔卡到<br />\n昆左同學既邪鬼"},{"pid":"ac03ce81b86f10e11d48faaf21930f6cc1e1c7de","tid":146022,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:21:02.000Z","msg":"當年重課左幾千銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe295f3f5a822508aa22cebd7ca64155148cfe1c","tid":146022,"uid":73348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:01:32.000Z","msg":"迪雲死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但抽中左小丹超必<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd90ad94b1656c91a8174c87dc3f3e0f1c49713","tid":146022,"uid":87429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"想當年我苦練隻亨利上到七十幾lv 俾條仆街仔昆左我ac走 好撚大童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c15a39330a522e6566cc20db92cc342cd9b1953","tid":146022,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩家姐朋友個ac<br />\n扔咗兩件裝（冰劍+一支黃色一碌嘢）<br />\n比我家姐屌撚死我..."},{"pid":"83bb8cf6f1b8ce86c6ea02e42d28108350927f18","tid":146022,"uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:1